IntFeature
public class AnnotationF
extends PhraseF
implements IntFeature

Turned on for phrases marked with a corresponding annotation. The annotation can be e.g. a syntactic chunk, a POS tag, an automatic label produced by preceding processors, or a manual attribute annotation in case of training data
